00:54:45,577 --> 00:54:48,080
Am I going to
lose my hair?

823
00:54:48,163 --> 00:54:48,830
Maybe.

824
00:54:48,914 --> 00:54:52,000
Maybe not. It varies
with each person.

825
00:54:53,043 --> 00:54:55,212
Let's do it!

826
00:54:55,295 --> 00:54:56,380
Good.

827
00:54:57,089 --> 00:54:58,006
When?

828
00:54:59,258 --> 00:55:01,718
I'm available
tomorrow evening.

829
00:55:01,802 --> 00:55:04,555
Oh, tomorrow evening is bad.
It's spaghetti and meatball night.

830
00:55:04,638 --> 00:55:06,098
Ben really looks forward...

831
00:55:06,181 --> 00:55:09,059
Okay, tomorrow's
good! Fine.

832
00:55:19,528 --> 00:55:21,572
Hi, honey.
How you doing?

833
00:55:21,655 --> 00:55:24,533
Mom, I've been
waiting for your call!

834
00:55:24,616 --> 00:55:27,119
- Mom, you're not gonna believe it!
- What?

835
00:55:27,202 --> 00:55:30,205
- I'm telepathetic!
- You mean, telepathic?

836
00:55:30,289 --> 00:55:32,082
That's what I said.

837
00:55:32,165 --> 00:55:34,084
I just discovered it today.

838
00:55:34,168 --> 00:55:36,128
I can read minds.

839
00:55:36,211 --> 00:55:37,421
No way.

840
00:55:37,504 --> 00:55:40,716
Yeah, I just tried it with Dad
and Isabel, and guess what?

841
00:55:40,799 --> 00:55:42,050
What?

842
00:55:42,134 --> 00:55:45,345
I always knew exactly
what they were thinking!

843
00:55:45,429 --> 00:55:47,222
That is incredible.

844
00:55:47,306 --> 00:55:49,266
- Want me to read yours?
- Absolutely.

845
00:55:49,516 --> 00:55:52,853
- Think real hard about something.
- I'm thinking.

846
00:55:52,936 --> 00:55:54,897
- Close your eyes.
- Ok.

847
00:55:55,939 --> 00:55:58,317
Concentrate.

848
00:55:58,400 --> 00:56:00,110
I am concentrating.

849
00:56:03,363 --> 00:56:05,490
You're thinking
about... me!

850
00:56:07,534 --> 00:56:09,620
That is amazing!

851
00:56:09,703 --> 00:56:11,371
What else?

852
00:56:11,455 --> 00:56:15,250
And you're wishing you were
here instead of where you are.

853
00:56:16,001 --> 00:56:18,086
That's for sure.

854
00:56:18,170 --> 00:56:20,464
Where are you, anyway?

855
00:56:20,547 --> 00:56:23,383
I'm in bed, with the flu...

856
00:56:23,467 --> 00:56:25,928
...and I'm green
and barfing.

857
00:56:26,011 --> 00:56:27,387
I knew that.

858
00:56:27,930 --> 00:56:30,390
And you're wishing you were
here making me spaghetti...

859
00:56:30,474 --> 00:56:33,727
...so I wouldn't have to eat
Daddy's sucky lamb chop.

860
00:56:33,810 --> 00:56:35,395
You're right about that.

861
00:56:35,479 --> 00:56:38,232
- See? I'm pathatelic!
- Telepathic!

862
00:56:38,941 --> 00:56:40,442
That's what I said.

863
00:56:42,819 --> 00:56:46,448
- When am I going to see you?
- Tomorrow after school.

864
00:56:47,783 --> 00:56:49,993
I was wishing I'd
see you tonight.

865
00:56:51,870 --> 00:56:53,705
Well, we'll just
gonna have...

866
00:56:53,789 --> 00:56:56,375
...to have one of our dream
dates and meet somewhere special.

867
00:56:56,458 --> 00:56:57,584
In our dreams!

868
00:56:57,668 --> 00:57:01,296
Where haven't we been in a
while? How about Disneyland?

869
00:57:01,380 --> 00:57:03,632
No... last time, the
lines were too long.

870
00:57:06,385 --> 00:57:07,636
The beach.

871
00:57:08,470 --> 00:57:10,097
Yeah!

872
00:57:10,180 --> 00:57:12,432
On a hot summer day.

873
00:57:12,516 --> 00:57:15,269
With gigantic waves.

874
00:57:15,352 --> 00:57:16,937
And boogie boards.

875
00:57:17,020 --> 00:57:18,897
And corn dogs.

876
00:57:18,981 --> 00:57:20,482
Awesome.

