878
00:57:26,196 --> 00:57:28,740
It's a dream, mom.
You don't need sunblock.

879
00:57:30,117 --> 00:57:31,869
That's right. I forgot!

880
00:57:33,996 --> 00:57:36,665
- Mommy, you still there?
- Yeah.

881
00:57:36,748 --> 00:57:38,417
Ben? Time for dinner.

